  "non_finch_justification": "We cannot ship two copies of ICU and switch with a flag as ICU is a very large library. Instead we have carefully analyzed test changes and added a flag for the risky change that we could identify in V8:\nhttps://chromium-review.googlesource.com/c/v8/v8/+/6944304\n\nThat flag can be controlled with Finch.",
  "ongoing_constraints": null,
  "rollout_plan": 0,
